niagara.utils
Class DuplicateHashtable

java.lang.Object
  niagara.utils.DuplicateHashtable

public class DuplicateHashtable
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides a hash table implementation in which many objects can be added with the same key. Thus a get, given a key, returns a list of objects rather than a single object as with the JDK1.2 hashtable

Version:
1.0
